pullRequest.body:
The first automated commit is the result of running
```find Mathlib -type f -exec sed -i -E "s/cases' (.*?) with ([^_]+) \2( |$)/rcases \1 with \2 | \2\3/g" {} \;```
Errors were then fixed manually, as well as the instances in the Archive and Counterexamples folders.

----

- [x] depends on: #16526
